                                <li>Audio-visual explanations for complex topics</li>
                                <li>Digital content to support classroom teaching</li>
                                <li>Real-time interaction between teachers and students</li>
                                <li>Better focus, clarity, and participation</li>
                                <li>Clear visual explanation of concepts</li>
                                <li>Engaging multimedia learning</li>
                                <li>Inclusive learning for all students</li>
                                <li>Active classroom participation</li>
