                    </div>

                    <div class=" col-sm-8 col-lg-8 d-flex justify-content-center mt-5">
                        <div class="sport_content_tab">
                            <h2 class="sport_title">We care about health, discipline, and overall growth — not just
                                marks</h2>
                            <p class="sport_content mt-5">Physical education plays an important role in a student’s
                                overall development.
                                Regular sports activities help students stay active, build discipline, and
                                develop teamwork and leadership qualities. Through structured games and
                                physical training, students learn the importance of fitness, focus, and a
                                healthy lifestyle.</p>
                            <p class="sport_content mt-4">Sports at our school focus on building strength, discipline,
                                and teamwork.
                                Regular physical activities help students stay active, confident, and focused,
                                supporting both physical health and mental well-being.</p>
                            <p class="sport_content mt-4">We believe a healthy body supports a healthy mind.
                                Through regular sports and physical activities, students develop fitness,
                                self-discipline, and teamwork while learning the value of an active and
                                balanced lifestyle.</p>


                        </div>
